{"tid":1573063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今天16號就係實施普教中咨詢deadline，大家幫手send send email","createTime":"2019-09-16T00:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T13:38:56.000Z","uid":191111,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8316618fc9c3fc7a38a2fc6fb0fb579b13f8237f","tid":1573063,"uid":191111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T00:51:33.000Z","msg":"⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠<br />\n大家幫幫手send email，今天16號就係實施普教中咨詢deadline，通過左就再無粵語教學‼<br />\n⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠⚠<br />\n無論大家咩政見，廣東話始終係我地由細到大嘅語言，大家一起幫手捍衛母語🙏🏼🙏🏼🙏🏼<br />\n電郵： taskforce_cur@edb.gov.hk<br />\n傳真號碼： (852) 2573 5299<br />\n<br />\n致專責小組成員：<br />\n本人為香港市民，有聞 貴組於6月28日文件中提出刪去文憑試聆聽及說話考卷，本人強烈反對，原因如下：<br />\n一，掌握母語不等於能以母語表達，說話要言之有物、出口成文，除了要豐富的詞彙，亦要有清晰的表達方式，說話卷的核心價值在於檢視學生在日常用語之外，能否有效建構論點展開討論，而廢除後則無地方訓練學生這頂基本能力。<br />\n二，掌握母語不等於能理解別人話語內容，聆聽別人的說話可以訓練學生將對話精煉的能力，亦即是捕捉重點的能力，假如廢除，恐怕學生會失去一個練習的平台，無法與人有效溝通。<br />\n三，以語言系公開試ielts雅思為例，考核學生英語水平以讀聽寫說四考卷，尤其是以說話難度最高，一向是該考試衡量英語高水平者的好標準，如今 貴組研廢除聆、說二卷，猶如自斷一臂。<br />\n綜合以上及眾多學者之言，冀 貴組於此項教育改革方向予於重新考慮。<br />\n<br />\n祝<br />\n工作順利"},{"pid":"0abe6fac59e0a6233c014d834ee9218ff2a02882","tid":1573063,"uid":233593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:32:41.000Z","msg":"廣東話要撐"},{"pid":"1f9d42e70a53c3d0832e97d69c53416a9730c2cd","tid":1573063,"uid":144942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:33:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6333dbf0f2429bf806c3177119964683f82e30c4","tid":1573063,"uid":282777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T02:42:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"832a083b06eb634161b78b58545e71d14bcd1bfb","tid":1573063,"uid":89013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:00:57.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"146ee465073c2a95bde6ddb1b49766ac84aced9f","tid":1573063,"uid":144797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T06:40:02.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f61e65ca48efc60fe74c66f1e1e3f5de9114ab48","tid":1573063,"uid":196422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:30:51.000Z","msg":"推 ~"},{"pid":"4eac58a5c7a2dc7050c81c7fc6e5bee7c6723fd9","tid":1573063,"uid":196422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:38:56.000Z","msg":"諮詢期延遲一個月，去到10月16<br />\n但香港人善忘，見到記住快d send email 💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/about-edb/press/consultation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edb.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fabout-edb%2Fpress%2Fconsultation&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=f5d824ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.edb.gov.hk/tc/about-edb/press/consultation</a>"}]}